{"type": "article", "id": 36416, "title": "检测水质的工具包，可爱又一目了然｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-04T23:00:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26212, "name": "Studio Lorier"}, {"id": 36470, "name": "Co-motion Studio"}, {"id": 36471, "name": "Onehundred"}, {"id": 36472, "name": "Assembli"}, {"id": 36473, "name": "Gerardo Osio"}, {"id": 36474, "name": "120WaterAudit"}, {"id": 36475, "name": "Universal Favourite"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170104224755FZjJa6VviPrOIWuU.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>120WaterAudit by Co-motion Studio</h3><p><a href=\"https://120wateraudit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">120WaterAudit</a> 是美国的一家面向企业和个人提供定期水质检测服务的公司，为了让整个过程变得简单明了，方便用户操作，他们联合创意机构 <a href=\"https://comotion.studio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Co-motion Studio</a> 设计了一套检测工具包和配套的包装系统。赏心悦目的蓝白主色调和各类与水质检测相关的小图标为工具包增添了亲和力，打开后用户可以看到同样由图标构成的操作说明和一个用来集水的瓶子、用于寄回公司的封带和可以留存的纪念贴纸等物品。如果你留心观察的话，会发现包装上外蓝白之间的分界线同时还对应了注水线所在的位置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224840xCdvOfkqoyelNX5A.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042248416183pbdicKAVDMZT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224840cuLCiKsPDrQ0e3fq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224840wA1CFePzROK2vlfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042248421U2fjYmPnMJ8Ltvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224841tLfzE7jiQnTad4KV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Spyn by Onehundred</h3><p>每一天我们都要作出各种各样的决定，摇摆不定总是在所难免。为了让做决定这件事变得有趣一些，来自美国的众筹产品制造商 <a href=\"http://www.onehundred.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Onehundred</a> 最近就推出了一套名叫 Spyn 的陀螺，其中三款的表面刻有选项，可以帮助你确定是/否、现在/稍后以及你/我这几类的问题。如果你要做的决定比较复杂（比如今晚吃什么），Onehundred 也提供了表面空白的陀螺供你用笔在上面 DIY。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/onehundred/spyn-decision-making-made-fun\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 24 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104225009jGtvPOR18Y7K2B9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104225009pjqGSKg2znB4cZRb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104225011MJXgdlBbuITzwRZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042250097L4hvKIXRfrWs0mJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104225010sMO1nr3DRfYqGEIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Beetle Kit by Assembli</h3><p>来自荷兰的 <a href=\"http://assembli.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assembli</a> 是一个由设计师 Joop Bource 和印刷公司 Lankhorst 合作推出的品牌，专门经营那些需要你动手的“室内项目”——之所以这么称呼，是因为与其将那些需要你花上一点时间才能拼出的纸雕称为“产品”，他们更希望称其为“项目”，强调专心制作一件物品的过程，并非结果。最近他们推出了三款以甲壳虫为原型的纸雕，从成品照片来看，的确相当还原。它们的部件均采用厚纸板制成，拼装大概需要 45 分钟的时间。你可以通过<a href=\"http://assembli.nl/online-shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 24.75 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224952w7UaIZf5RknxSPND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669231\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224952J4U6ptDiCVvN0wgT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224952Q36BhUHt072S1EeY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224953uiSvzN8PUj1LxgBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.956923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hybrid Chair by Studio Lorier</h3><p>还记得那个会因为重心往后倾斜，提醒你加水的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/34873.html\">花盆</a>吗？它背后的设计师 <a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sander Lorier</a> 来自荷兰，特别擅长利用重心巧妙地对常见的生活用品进行改造，让它们变得更加实用。继自动浇水花盆之后，他又推出了一款多功能的混合椅 <a href=\"http://studiolorier.com/product/hybrid-chair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hybrid Chair</a>。借助椅背上的纺织带以及可以滑动的木质结构，能够在写字椅和躺椅之间灵活切换。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224938yaSOrcNmPsBq6QID.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224937H98EVOqF74N5iIvg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042249378C2ejHt9wSrglTIJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224937FSXEoiskW53CpKvu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nomadic Life Kit by Gerardo Osio</h3><p>在过去的一年中，我们介绍过好几款针对“游牧型”生活方式所设计的模块化产品，轻质和易组装是它们主打的两大特色。和大件家具不同，由设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.gerardoosio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gerardo Osio</a> 推出的“游牧生活”（<a href=\"http://www.gerardoosio.com/#/nomadic-life/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nomadic Life</a>）套装并不打算重塑一整个房间，而是希望能够帮助人们在任何地方都能创造出熟悉的生活环境。设计师以佛教和神道教为灵感，和六个日本传统手工艺工作室合作，利用天然的材料制作了一套风格朴素的生活用品，包括稻草垫、靠垫、铜质餐具、烛台、花瓶和一个木箱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224922DEM9yC7JdfepV8R4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.729333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224921p6ujeXWl1sEMZDvk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224921QC8koxSMfZqD0Je2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042249211Hqm8Yj4A3efSUC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224921KQwafbgh6sL5Btcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224921IYDcCRMmUL67Bar9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Complements chocolates by Universal Favourite</h3><p>圣诞加上年末，很多公司都会专门制作一份感谢礼物赠给客户。澳大利亚创意公司 <a href=\"http://universalfavourite.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Universal Favorite</a> 去年就和悉尼甜品店 <a href=\"http://www.bakedowncakery.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bakedown Cakery</a> 合作，利用 3D 打印技术制作了一批五彩缤纷的模块化巧克力。这些巧克力看上去就像是一段台阶，可以两两组合在一起，以此传达出设计师与客户之间的合作关系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701042248219CuDycVbZi8xAaQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747885\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224823qGQST3hbJju5K8aN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224822Inc0p4jRvtY78FUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.104907\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104224823XtRZTkrUp98Om4Iv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.088409\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}